评论概述: Doesn’t turn finger green, but DOES tarnish
评论详情: I bought this ring partially because of the style and partially because of all the claims that it’s tarnish-free and waterproof. It looks exactly as pictured and fits appropriately, but it DOES tarnish. It didn’t turn my finger green, but the reddish tarnish color is visible on the sides of the rings. It almost looks like the sides and back of the ring have been repeatedly scratched by other jewelry, but they haven’t. The top of the ring still looks okay, but I do find it disappointing that this ring hasn’t even lasted 2 weeks. I guess it’s worth the money *technically* because it looks and feels nice for being cheap, but I had much higher expectations. Amazon wants me to mention the weight, so I will say that it feels high quality but not overly heavy.
